snippet.title: Fight School Simulator - trailer
snippet.description:
Step into the world of Martial Arts, an immersive FPS Simulation where you take on the role of a martial arts instructor determined to build the ultimate dojo. From humble beginnings, guide to greatness by mastering martial arts, teaching the next generation of fighters, and standing up to rivals.
